Page Window

Located within the Page Editor

The Page Window is used to view & update page information, including keywords, description, and security. The Page CSS tab includes a code editor so you can add custom CSS & LESS code to your page.

The icon located on the Page Editor toolbar's page button is a faded ring with four faded circles and one blue circle. The faded ring represents the web site as a whole, while the faded circles represents all the pages within the web site and the blue circle represents a single page.
